4.	Unscrew the 3-pin connector that is included in the packing list and the RS232 to RS485 adapter;
5.	Insert one end of the DuPont wires to the RS232 to RS485 adapter and the other end to the 3-pin connector following the pinout described in the prior step, then tighten the screws;

